### 5c · Placeholder Formats

All file templates use these placeholders consistently:

| Placeholder  | Format             | Example            |
| ------------ | ------------------ | ------------------ |
| `{DATE}`     | `YYYY-MM-DD`       | `2026-03-01`       |
| `{DATETIME}` | `YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm` | `2026-03-01 14:30` |
| `{N}`        | Integer            | `7`                |
| `{PCT}`      | Integer, no decimals | `60`             |
| `{TOTAL}`    | Integer            | `12`               |

All times are in the user's local timezone. If unknown, use UTC and note it.

